name: Spikka - The Fortune Teller
description:
Piece Of Cake collectible Esoteric cards starring Goddesses and Daemons.

Spikka the Fortune Teller can be seen anywhere in the Tezos Blockchain after midnight.
Do not let her read your fortune telling cards in any manner. Her only goal is to deceive you.
If she offers it to you, the only right answer is : "I am my own Fortune Teller".
